## Architecture — Stateless Execution Pattern

Each tool is a pure function. Same input always produces same output. No shared
state. No side effects. Determinism guaranteed.

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> idle
    idle --> running: tool.invoke
    running --> completed: success
    running --> failed: error
    completed --> idle
    failed --> idle
```

## Install

```bash
npm install
npm run build
```

## Run

### Standalone (stdio)
```bash
npm start
```

### Claude Desktop / Cursor
Add to your MCP config:
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{name}}": {
      "command": "node",
      "args": ["dist/index.js"]
    }
  }
}
```

## Test

```bash
npm test                    # unit + contract
npm run test:property       # property-based (fast-check)
npm run test:mutation       # mutation testing (stryker)
```

